<div class="welcome-container">
  <h1>About GameLog</h1>
  <p>
    GameLog is a full-stack web application built for the "Databases and the Web" coursework. It demonstrates how to create a modern, data-driven site from scratch.
  </p>

  <h2>Core Technologies</h2>
  <p>
    • <strong>Node.js & Express:</strong> Server runtime and framework for routing and middleware.  
    • <strong>EJS:</strong> Templating engine that injects server data into HTML.  
    • <strong>MySQL:</strong> Relational database storing all user and review information.
  </p>

  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <p>
    • Search games via the public RAWG API.  
    • Secure user signup/login and personalized review library.  
    • Built-in API endpoint to share library data programmatically.
  </p>
</div>

